# Claudot Bridge Configuration
# No configuration is required here.
#
# - The default "Claude Code" provider uses Claude Code CLI's OAuth
#   authentication automatically (~/.claude).
# - Bring-your-own-API-key providers (Anthropic API, OpenAI, custom) are
#   configured from the Godot editor: Claudot panel > Settings. Keys are
#   stored in Godot's editor settings, outside the project, and pushed to
#   the bridge over loopback TCP — never written to this directory.
#
# This file exists as a placeholder. If future features require environment
# variables, they will be documented here.
